From 4ac76f0b158ac4d183b62d40d2748fbc3dd95c67 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Brad Larson <bradley.larson@amd.com>
Date: Wed, 24 Jun 2026 12:50:23 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 10/20] i2c: designware: add AMD Pensando support

Add Pensando-specific support to the DesignWare I2C driver: stuck SDA
line recovery, a slave-mode FIFO configuration stub and dynamic
master/slave switching.

The stuck SDA line recovery is based on work by David Clear.

Signed-off-by: Brad Larson <bradley.larson@amd.com>
